snippet.title: 7 Billion Humans - Now Available! - Official Trailer #2
snippet.description:
Now available on Win/Mac/Linux on all stores. Automate swarms of office workers to solve puzzles inside your very own parallel computer made of people. ...a thrilling followup to the award winning Human Resource Machine. Now with more humans! 

More info: http://tomorrowcorporation.com/7billionhumans
On Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/792100/7_Billion_Humans/
On GoG: https://www.gog.com/game/7_billion_humans_pack
On Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/7-billion-humans

Music by Kyle Gabler.

(c) Tomorrow Corporation
